# AggregationInterval

Time interval which will be used for aggregation. Can be `Hour`, `Day`, `Week` or `Month`

**Properties**

| Name  | Type | Required | Description |
| :---- | :--- | :------- | :---------- |
| HOUR  | str  | ✅       | "Hour"      |
| DAY   | str  | ✅       | "Day"       |
| WEEK  | str  | ✅       | "Week"      |
| MONTH | str  | ✅       | "Month"     |
